{"word":"G398 - ἀναφαίνω - anaphaínō - an-af-ah'-ee-no - Appear","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀναφαίνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">anaphaínō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">an-af-ah'-ee-no</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Appear</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வெளிப்படு, காண்"},{"paragraph":"to bring to light, hold up to view, show"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G303 - ἀνά - aná - an-ah'/303\">G303</a> and <a href=\"#/G5316 - φαίνω - phaínō - fah'-ee-no/5316\">G5316</a>; to <i>show</i>, that is, (reflexively) <i>appear</i>, or (passively) <i>have pointed</i> out: - (should) appear, discover.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}